The tiger bid his appetizers to sit and wait for him, making his way to the waters to meet his polite addresser. What a scary sight. “Who called me?” Grumbling, he looks down and notices an object resembling a small wooden plate. “Could this have called me?” He set a giant paw on the turtles middle until he turtle squeals “Ouch!”. The tiger grinned. “Oh, the most aphrodisiac Korean turtle soup I’ve always wanted. How lucky I am!”.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
