EVTDESC_KO_640.3;The turtle groans and thinks of a plan. Stretching his neck out all the way, he screams. “Beast, you don’t know who I am or why I am here. I’ve come for the cure for the Sea King’s ills! He will reward you with dolphin cutlet if you leave me be.” Intrigued the tiger lets the turtle summon the hare and the two escape. “Where are you taking me?” asks the hare, looking around.“I will take you to the dragon palace”. The turtle described Dragon Palace and all the good things inside and the rabbit was enchanted. When they arrived the hare was so excited he sung and danced. Soon it was reported the hare had arrived and he was seized by the guards..
